---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import {
  TRON_RECEIVER_ADDRESS,
  TRONSCAN_ADDRESS_URL,
  PRICE_WITH_U,
  PRICE_WITHOUT_U,
} from "../config/site";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title={`【官方】TRX能量租赁 - ${PRICE_WITH_U}/${PRICE_WITHOUT_U} TRX/笔，波场转账省80%手续费`}
  description={`专业波场TRX能量租赁平台，USDT(TRC20)转账有U地址仅需${PRICE_WITH_U} TRX，无U地址${PRICE_WITHOUT_U} TRX。即时自动到账，安全可靠，大幅降低您的链上交易成本。`}
  keywords="TRX能量租赁,波场能量租赁,TRON能量租赁,USDT转账手续费,TRC20能量,波场TRX,能量闪租,TRX25"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section id="hero" class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 text-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
      </span>
      全自动 AI 派发，24/7 在线
    </div>
    
    <h1 id="price-title" class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] mb-6">
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-gray-200 to-gray-500">波场转账</span><br />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-indigo-400 to-purple-400">立省 80% 手续费</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl font-light leading-relaxed">
      USDT (TRC20) 转账能量按笔计费。无需繁琐授权，向指定地址转入 TRX 即可<strong class="text-gray-200 font-medium">秒级自动到账</strong>。
    </p>
    
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
      <a class="btn btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-base shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(59,130,246,0.25)] hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(59,130,246,0.4)]" href="#address">
        获取收款地址
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-base" href="#steps">
        查看使用教程
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Section -->
  <section id="price" aria-labelledby="sec-plans" class="mb-20 md:mb-32 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 id="sec-plans" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">极简定价，拒绝套路</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">根据接收方地址状态，系统自动匹配最优能量方案。</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Plan 1 -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500/20 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur-xl transition-all duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100 opacity-0"></div>
        <div class="relative h-full bg-[#0a0f1c] border border-blue-500/30 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-500"></div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-6">
            常规推荐
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-300 font-medium mb-2">对方地址已有 U</h3>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white">{PRICE_WITH_U}</span>
            <span class="text-xl text-gray-500 font-medium">TRX / 笔</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            适用于绝大多数普通 USDT 转账场景。<br />系统将自动派发约 65,000 能量。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Plan 2 -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-500/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur-xl transition-all duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100 opacity-0"></div>
        <div class="relative h-full bg-[#0a0f1c] border border-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-gray-700">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-gray-800 text-gray-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-6">
            首次激活
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-300 font-medium mb-2">对方地址无 U</h3>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white">{PRICE_WITHOUT_U}</span>
            <span class="text-xl text-gray-500 font-medium">TRX / 笔</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            适用于新地址或当前无 USDT 余额的地址。<br />系统将自动派发约 131,000 能量。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works Section -->
  <section id="steps" aria-labelledby="sec-steps" class="mb-20 md:mb-32 scroll-mt-24 relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-900/5 rounded-[3rem] -z-10 transform -rotate-1"></div>
    <div class="bg-[#0a0f1c]/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 rounded-[3rem] p-8 md:p-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <h2 id="sec-steps" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">简单 3 步，轻松获取</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">无需注册，无需授权，转账即用。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12 relative">
        <!-- 连接线 (仅在大屏显示) -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-8 left-[15%] right-[15%] h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/0 via-blue-500/20 to-blue-500/0 -z-10"></div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-gray-900 border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-blue-400 mb-6 shadow-lg">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-200 mb-3">复制地址</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">复制本页提供的官方收款地址，并在您的去中心化钱包中准备转账。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/40 to-indigo-900/40 border border-blue-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-blue-400 mb-6 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(59,130,246,0.2)]">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-200 mb-3">转入 TRX</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">根据对方地址是否有 U，向收款地址转入 {PRICE_WITH_U} 或 {PRICE_WITHOUT_U} TRX。务必确认网络为 TRON。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-gray-900 border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-blue-400 mb-6 shadow-lg">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-200 mb-3">自动到账</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">链上确认后（通常 3-9 秒），系统会自动将能量派发到您发起转账的钱包中。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Address Section (核心转化区) -->
  <section id="address" aria-labelledby="sec-address" class="mb-20 md:mb-32 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 rounded-3xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-[#0a0f1c] border border-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
          <h2 id="sec-address" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">官方收款地址</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-8">支持 TronLink, TokenPocket, imToken 等去中心化钱包</p>
          
          <div class="bg-black/50 border border-gray-800/80 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6 mb-6">
            <div class="font-mono text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl break-all text-blue-300 selection:bg-blue-500/30" id="tron-address" translate="no">
              {TRON_RECEIVER_ADDRESS}
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-base" id="copy-address-btn">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 16H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v2m-6 12h8a2 2 0 002-2v-8a2 2 0 00-2-2h-8a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
              一键复制地址
            </button>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-base" href={TRONSCAN_ADDRESS_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              在 TronScan 上验证
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 opacity-70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 text-xs sm:text-sm">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path></svg>
            <span class="text-left">警告：只接受 TRX 转账！切勿从交易所直接转账，否则无法到账。</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Grid -->
  <section aria-labelledby="sec-advantages" class="mb-20 md:mb-32">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="glass-card flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 border border-blue-500/20">⚡</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">毫秒级响应</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">全节点自建服务，链上确认后系统毫秒级触发派发，告别漫长等待。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 border border-indigo-500/20">💎</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">百亿能量池</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">平台自有海量 TRX 质押池，保障 24 小时能量供应充足，永不断档。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 border border-purple-500/20">🔒</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">绝对安全</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">纯链上转账交互，无需连接钱包，不索要任何授权，100% 资产安全。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card flex flex-col items-start">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 border border-emerald-500/20">🤖</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">无人值守</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">AI 智能合约全自动处理订单，节假日无休，随时随地满足转账需求。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section aria-labelledby="sec-faq" class="mb-20 md:mb-32">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-16">
      <h2 id="sec-faq" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">常见问题解答</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">了解更多关于波场能量租赁的细节</p>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>为什么能量租赁有两种价格？</summary>
        <p>
          波场网络规则决定，接收方地址若无 USDT 余额或首次激活，消耗能量会更高（约 13.1万）。有 U 地址仅需约 6.5万 能量。我们提供两种价格覆盖不同场景，确保您的转账成本最优。
        </p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>怎么判断对方地址是否「有 U」？</summary>
        <p>简单来说，如果对方地址从未收到过 USDT (TRC20) 或当前余额为零，可视为「无 U」地址。最准确的方法是前往 TronScan.org 查询该地址的 USDT 余额或历史交易记录。如果不确定，建议按「无 U」价格转账以防能量不足。</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>转账到收款地址后，能量多久能到账？</summary>
        <p>我们的系统全自动监控，通常在您的 TRX 转账完成后，等待 1-3 个区块确认（约 3-9 秒），能量即可自动派发到您发起转账的钱包地址。网络拥堵时可能略有延迟，但请放心，系统会确保处理。</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>如果我转错了金额或转到了错误的链怎么办？</summary>
        <p>波场 (TRON) 链上交易具有<strong>不可逆性</strong>。一旦转账完成，资金将无法追回。请务必在转账前仔细核对收款地址、转账网络（必须是 TRON）以及转账金额。<strong>切勿将资金转入其他区块链网络或非本页公示的地址。</strong></p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>能量租赁能节省多少手续费？</summary>
        <p>通过租赁能量，您可以避免在 TRC20 转账时因能量不足而燃烧 TRX。以一笔标准 TRC20 转账为例，如果没有能量，可能需要燃烧约 14 TRX 或更高。通过我们的服务，您仅需支付 {PRICE_WITH_U} 或 {PRICE_WITHOUT_U} TRX，<strong>最高可节省约 80% 的手续费</strong>。</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item" name="faq">
        <summary>我可以使用哪个钱包进行操作？</summary>
        <p>您可以使用任何支持 TRON (波场) 网络和 TRC20 代币的去中心化钱包，例如 TronLink, TokenPocket, imToken, SafePal 等。<strong>请勿直接从交易所转账 TRX 到我们的收款地址</strong>，以免系统无法识别您的能量需求并导致资产损失。</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer Note -->
  <div class="border-t border-gray-800/50 pt-8 pb-4">
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      <strong>免责声明：</strong> 本平台仅提供基于波场 TRON 网络的能量租赁技术服务。链上操作不可逆，用户需自行承担因地址填错、网络选错等操作失误造成的资产损失。本站不提供任何法定货币兑换服务，不构成任何投资或金融建议。
    </p>
  </div>

  <script define:vars={{ tronAddr: TRON_RECEIVER_ADDRESS }}>
    (function () {
      var btn = document.getElementById("copy-address-btn");
      if (!btn) return;
      btn.addEventListener("click", function () {
        function ok() {
          var originalHTML = btn.innerHTML;
          btn.innerHTML = '<svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> 复制成功';
          btn.classList.add('bg-green-900/30', 'border-green-500/50', 'text-green-400');
          btn.classList.remove('btn-primary');
          
          setTimeout(function () {
            btn.innerHTML = originalHTML;
            btn.classList.remove('bg-green-900/30', 'border-green-500/50', 'text-green-400');
            btn.classList.add('btn-primary');
          }, 2000);
        }
        if (navigator.clipboard && navigator.clipboard.writeText) {
          navigator.clipboard.writeText(tronAddr).then(ok).catch(function () {
            window.prompt("请手动复制：", tronAddr);
          });
        } else {
          window.prompt("请手动复制：", tronAddr);
        }
      });
    })();
  </script>
</Layout>

